  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Position Trend</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio07fbc5536a51204be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\"> Position Trend </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> The position trend list provides an overview of the position trends both on and off the balance sheet in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Manager</span> between two key dates specified by the user.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The report serves as a standard list that you can use as it is or as a template for creating your own reports.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Integration\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Integration</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> This report is a query. The query is based on InfoSet /SAPQUERY/CFM_PERIODS, which in turn is based on logical database FTI_TR_PERIODS.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The technical name of this query is CFM_PER_02.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Features\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Features</h2>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Selection</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"b6fac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Product Groups</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"ddfac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Selections</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"adfac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Control Parameters</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Output</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The list is displayed using the SAP List Viewer.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also:</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4dd40b7ac2234be2e10000000a42189c.html\" title=\"\">SAP List Viewer for SAP GUI (Classic)</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}